divs: Sighting DetailsI came out of mall, and two people were staring up at sky, so I stopped to look too. The woman said there was a ufo. Sure enough there was a weird moving light that was flashing, sometimes white, then red, but it wasn't moving straight. I watched it for about a minute. And then it disappeared. It was cloudy. There was no noise. Interesting.
